OL,3,CParish council silences church bells
OL,4,Cafter complaint from angry villager
OL,6,FWitheridge Parish Council has paid
OL,7,Fmore than #2,000 to install a night
OL,8,Fsilencer, to stop the bells from
OL,9,Fringing between 11pm and 7am.
OL,11,FThe silencer was fitted on Friday 15
OL,12,FMarch. It means the bells chime only
OL,13,Fbetween 7am and 11pm.
OL,15,FNorth East Devon Council said officers
OL,16,Ffrom the Environmental Protection Team
OL,17,Fassessed the noise level from the
OL,18,Fclock bells before serving a noise
OL,19,Fabatement notice.
