OL,3,CParish council silences church bells
OL,4,Cafter complaint from angry villager
OL,6,FThe officers determined the noise was
OL,7,Floud enough to be a "Statutory
OL,8,FNuisance under Section 79(g) of the
OL,9,FEnvironmental Protection Act 1990," a
OL,10,Fcouncil spokesperson said.
OL,12,F"They considered the loudness, the
OL,13,Ffrequency and duration of the noise.
OL,14,FIt was considered that the chime every
OL,15,F15 minutes was likely to wake or
OL,16,Fdisturb the sleep of the complainant
OL,17,Fand other residents nearby."
